---
slug: "airport-transfer"
permalink: "/es/airport-transfer/index.html"
title: "Airport transfer | Morrison Premium Transfer"
description: "Airport pickup and onward transfer to the city or another region: flight tracking, baggage support, night arrivals, intercity continuation."
schema: "Service"
serviceType: "Airport private transfer"
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Inicio", path: "/es/" }
  - { name: "Airport", path: "/es/airport-transfer/" }
faq:
  - q: "How do you know the flight is delayed?"
    a: "From the flight number you give at booking, we track the status. If delayed — the driver arrives at the new ETA, no waiting surcharge."
  - q: "Where exactly will I be met?"
    a: "At the arrivals exit. Exact spot and driver contact arrive an hour before landing."
  - q: "Can I stop for errands on the way?"
    a: "Yes. Intermediate stops are listed at booking and factored into the timing. Price is fixed upfront."
  - q: "What if I have lots of luggage or children?"
    a: "Vehicle class is matched to luggage and passengers. Child seat on request at booking."
---
